  "title": "Line",
  "description": "Mutable line segment defined by two endpoint positions. Implements ShapeLike for intersection tests against all shape types. Note: `collidesWith` always returns `null` — lines support boolean intersection only; SAT response is not implemented for line segments. `contains(x, y, threshold)` tests whether `(x, y)` lies on the segment within a configurable threshold (default `0.1`). `Line.temp` is a shared scratch instance.",
